Network Packet Analyzer (Scapy)

This is a simple Python-based network packet analyzer built using Scapy.

The program captures live network packets and displays:

Source IP

Destination IP

Protocol (TCP/UDP)

Source & Destination Ports

DNS Queries and Responses

Installation
pip install scapy

Run the Script

On Windows:

python filename.py


On Linux:

sudo python3 filename.py


⚠️ Run with administrator/root privileges.
